Title: Private Property
Produced by: Chadd Harbold Shiloh Fernandez , Greg Lauritano Lucas Jarach Ryan R. Johnson Luke Daniels Shaun Sanghani
Production: Filming wrapped in Los Angeles in August 2021.
Release: The film was had a limited release in theaters and was fully released on demand and digital on May 13, 2022.
Reception: The film received negative reviews. It has a 13% rating on Rotten Tomatoes based on eight reviews.
